Financial Counseling


Holistic, comprehensive financial planning and education.





We are one of the nation's leading providers of comprehensive financial counseling for executives, employees and entrepreneurs.




Who We Support






C-Suite Executives





Mid-Level Executives





All Employee Populations



At any level of your career, you:

Are engaged in all aspects of your life
Are a steward of financial security for you and those you love
Value and appreciate quality
Strive for lifelong goal of financial wellness





We Add Value





To companies
Increased employee focus & satisfaction



To clients
Trusted Advisor & Financial Wellness







Management relationship tool designed to focus, engage and align each employee with the company through integrated financial planning.

Reduces employee's time spent on personal finances and allows them to focus on their work responsibilities
Helps maximize compensation and benefit plans
Enhances loyalty and retention
Facilitates compliance and adherence to company policies and procedures




Relationship-driven, holistic financial planning through education and guided implementation.

Practical application of knowledge through guided implementation
Ongoing education
Assistance in maximizing compensation and benefit plans





Areas of Focus




Cash-Flow Planning
Tax Preparation*
Retirement Planning
Tax-Planning Strategies
Investment Planning
Risk Management
Estate Planning

* Not all Financial Counseling offerings permit tax preparation.




Omni-channel platform with individual choice of access:





One-on-One Financial Counseling



Phone Counseling




In-Person Seminars and Webinars



Digital Tools Combined with Education






Digital Tools Which Can Provide:

Customized Reporting
Data Aggregation
Counselor Access
Your Customized Solution





There's a difference between ordinary financial planning and Ayco Financial Planning.
Simply put, we're built for this.





Breadth of Technical Knowledge



