Ayco | Family Office




































×


You are leaving The Ayco Company, L.P. corporate website to go to a site sponsored and maintained by a third-party vendor.


Continue







Family Office


Strategic integration for your life.





We understand the challenges you face and your desire to spend time pursuing other business or personal interests. We take a practical approach to addressing the complexities of wealth to give you greater peace of mind.




We know your time is at a premium and that your daily challenges may include:

Lack of time
Endless paperwork
Trying to coordinate scattered assets and accounts
Constant solicitations
Challenges with keeping up on the latest trends
The overall cost and overhead of services
Having misallocation of assets
Concerns about financial risk



How Ayco can help relieve burdens of wealth:

Summarizing decisions that need to be made and implementing action items
Completing paperwork and executing decisions
Providing customized financial exhibits and electronic filing system
Working with multiple generations and coordinating estate plans
Becoming your trusted advisor and acting as a gatekeeper
Providing sophisticated advice and coordinating with outside advisors
Leveraging firm resources while providing you with one dedicated team
Safeguarding your assets with appropriate checks and balances




We are one of the nation's leading providers of comprehensive financial management for institutions, not-for-profits, high-net-worth individuals and their families.




Family Office Facts

Time-Tested
Established in 1983
Powerful
We create a one-stop, personal CFO to help manage our client's financial affairs.
Resourceful
The essence of our Family Office is in the strategic thought process, idea generation, decision making and guided implementation.
National Focus
We advise clients in 44 states* and have regional offices in Chicago, Dallas and San Francisco.
Multigenerational
We often provide services to several different generations within one client family.
Coordination
We work with all other advisors as desired to ensure coordinated planning and execution.
Personalized
Each Client Advisor works with between 8 and 12 families.

* As of November 2014


Our Services
Your Ayco team can provide cohesiveness and coordinated planning around the following disciplines:


Tax Planning & Preparation
Investment Services
Risk Management
Generational Planning
Employee Benefit Services
Trust & Foundation Services
Consolidated Reporting
Philanthropic Planning
Cash Management & Bill Pay
Estate Planning





Ayco's approach provides the critical integration of these disciplines, eliminating the need for you to manage the details between your existing advisors.




Our Approach


Our Family Office approach creates a culture of individualized, results-driven financial management and integration for our clients and their families. Our teams work with an average of 8-12 clients. We are able to provide resources at the highest level of service to help save you time and money.
We coordinate your financial details.
We partner with your existing advisors to coordinate and maintain successful relationships.
You benefit from the combination of a larger firm—the experience of helping 200+ client families—with the personalized approach of a smaller family office.




How it works




Your dedicated Ayco team is led by your Ayco Advisor which can include an Ayco investment representative who would act as your personal Chief Investment Officer (CIO).
Your Ayco Advisor is supported by other professionals to assist with your various needs:

Proactive estate-planning solutions with a team dedicated to constantly researching current market trends.
Risk-management solutions which integrate insurance into the design and implementation of wealth-protection and wealth-transfer strategies.
A tax presence to help advise on complicated tax issues as well as assist with the preparation of highly complex tax returns.






In partnership with your Ayco advisor, your CIO can:

Provide objective investment advice
Analyze your existing holdings
Discuss market and macroeconomic events
Help create your portfolio strategy regardless of where your assets are held
Assist with implementation of tactical asset allocation based on investment goals and objectives
Conduct ongoing review and monitoring of portfolio





Simply put, we provide:





Strategic & Tactical Planning



Guided Implementation



Operational Execution






Our business is built and sustained on personal relationships. We are a resource and a partner for you and your family.
Let us get to work for you.




Get Started >


















